i ask the questions.
You answer the questions.

360
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:50,821
No long speeches.
Just keep it simple.

361
00:33:50,932 --> 00:33:52,058
Got it?

362
00:33:55,236 --> 00:33:57,067
Who are you?

363
00:33:57,171 --> 00:33:59,162
My name is Lai.
i come from Chi--

364
00:33:59,273 --> 00:34:00,740
Uhh!

365
00:34:00,842 --> 00:34:03,811
i ask the questions.
You answer the questions.

366
00:34:03,911 --> 00:34:05,503
Nothing more.
Nothing less.

367
00:34:05,613 --> 00:34:07,945
You want to try again?

368
00:34:12,086 --> 00:34:13,417
What kind of shit am i in?

369
00:34:13,521 --> 00:34:15,853
Deep shit.
Very deep shit.

370
00:34:15,957 --> 00:34:17,925
Those guys--
Sorry! Sorry!

371
