if i want to know everything...

537
00:44:44,318 --> 00:44:46,445
or nothing about you.

538
00:44:54,928 --> 00:44:56,520
What?

539
00:44:56,630 --> 00:44:58,029
The quiet.

540
00:44:58,131 --> 00:45:00,395
